olor": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/22275027"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0Ik/Oi/crfx+kmEAMaBzEwOTA5MjYgr/CwlQUwADjSA0AQcggyMjI3NTAyN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1775372882.255894", "card_id": "Q_2022807584403465039", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "吉利汽车一季度销量突破 70.9 万辆，创同期新高，这释放了哪些市场信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 1 日，吉利汽车集团公布了最新一期的销量情况。数据显示，2026 年第一季度，吉利汽车累计销量达 709,358 辆，创同期历史新高；其中 3 月单月销量为 233,031 辆，环比增长 13%。 从销量结构来看，新能源渗透率的稳步提升与海外出口的快速增长成为其销量增长的两大主力。 一季度，吉利汽车新能源累计销量 369,059 辆，渗透率达 52%，3 月单月渗透率进一步升至 55%。同期，其海外出口累计 203,024 辆，同比增幅达 126%，出口增速显著高于整体销量增速。 图片来源：吉利汽车 燃油基盘稳固，高端品牌增速分化 在品牌层面，吉利采取多品牌差异化定位策略，各品牌在能源类型与目标市场 吉利汽车一季度销量突破 70.9 万辆，创同期新高"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-2a2bde902fc075318c5905ff38a7525f.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022807584403465039"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIk/Oi/crfx+kmEAMaCTExODk4Nzc4MyC+4LTOBjAAOJIBQBFyEzIwMjI4MDc1ODQ0MDM0NjUwMzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1775372882.257609", "card_id": "Q_1991639712142758139", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 70}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中国大型城市当中空置的写字楼最后的结局会是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在北上广深等城市当中目前各类写字楼都有极高的空置率，这一情况是什么原因造成的？未来将会如何发展？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3f60346a64d2df88dc5f74263ec8ca1e_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/qu